title: Leo Thethani
text:
Leo Thethani (born 8 January 1999) is a South African professional <a href="association%20football">football</a> <a href="Forward%20%28association%20football%29">forward</a>. He plays in the Netherlands for <a href="Jong%20Ajax">Jong Ajax</a>.
Club career.
Thethani made his <a href="Eerste%20Divisie">Eerste Divisie</a> debut for <a href="Jong%20Ajax">Jong Ajax</a> on 10 September 2018 in a game against <a href="Jong%20AZ">Jong AZ</a> as a 78th-minute substitute for <a href="Danilo%20%28footballer%2C%20born%201999%29">Danilo</a>.
